&nbsp;

Concerns were brought up about where the funds from the Bill Lord Golf Tournament go.  There were concerns about how it is advertised if the funds do not fully fund the scholarship fund.  Anyone knowing the history behind this event please let me know at <a href="mailto:queenbee929@msn.com">queenbee929@msn.com</a>.

