We have a wonderful chapter and one of my main goals this year is to increase involvement from our inactive membership.  If you have any ideas on how to reach out to our membership and increase active involvement with our chapter please contact a board member or me.

&nbsp;

Don’t forget the fall workshop and OR nurse’s day at the museum.  To help with either event contact Peggy Camp for the fall workshop and Nancy Johnson for the day at the museum.  Hope to see many of you at both events.

